Class SysEx

  • java.lang.Object
    • jm.midi.event.SysEx
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Event, SysComEvt

    public final class SysEx
extends java.lang.Object
implements SysComEvt
    SysEx is an interfaced by Event and contains a tracks System Exclusive events. The system exclusive message is saved in a ByteList called message.
